---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="PostgreSQL React Integration | Enterprise Data Layer Best Practices"
  description="PostgreSQL React integration patterns for enterprise applications from TESCO Stores CZ implementation."
>
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-12">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="text-sm text-slate-400">
      <a href="/" class="transition hover:text-accent">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-2">→</span>
      <a href="/vocabulary" class="transition hover:text-accent">Vocabulary</a>
      <span class="mx-2">→</span>
      <span class="text-slate-200">PostgreSQL + React</span>
    </nav>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <p class="eyebrow">Backend Integration</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white sm:text-5xl">PostgreSQL + React Integration</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">Relational database connectivity for React apps</p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-[32px] border border-accent/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-transparent p-8 shadow-card">
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-100">
        <strong class="text-white">Definition:</strong> Connecting React frontends to PostgreSQL databases via REST or GraphQL APIs for relational data management in enterprise applications.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="surface-card space-y-6">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Architecture Patterns</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-200">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">API layer:</strong> React → Java/PHP REST API → PostgreSQL</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Type safety:</strong> TypeScript interfaces match database schema</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Data fetching:</strong> React Query or SWR for caching</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Performance:</strong> Connection pooling and query optimization</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="surface-card space-y-6">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow text-accent">Case Study</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Real Implementation: TESCO</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-200">
        The <strong class="text-white">TESCO Stores CZ operations portal</strong> connects React/TypeScript frontend to Java REST APIs backed by PostgreSQL, handling store operations, inventory, and campaign planning data.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Related Vocabulary</h3>
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <a href="/vocabulary/mongodb-react-dashboard" class="grid-panel">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-accent">MongoDB React Dashboard</h4>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Alternative database approach</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/vocabulary/internal-portal-development" class="grid-panel">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-accent">Internal Portal Development</h4>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Full-stack portal architecture</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-[32px] border border-accent/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-transparent p-8 text-center shadow-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Need Database Integration?</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-slate-200">I connect React frontends to PostgreSQL, MySQL, and MongoDB databases.</p>
      <a href="mailto:marekdolnicek@gmail.com" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-full bg-accent px-8 py-3 font-semibold text-ink shadow-card transition hover:bg-accentMuted">Contact me</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
